  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>To compare the yield of detecting metastatic prostate cancer tissue using MRI-guided bone marrow needle biopsies to that of historical controls obtained through unguided biopsies.</measure>
  </primary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>To evaluate the sensitivity of radiographic bone marrow changes detected by MRI for prostate cancer, as determined by the pathologic findings from bone marrow biopsy.</measure>
  </secondary_outcome>
